	5.	Conclusion

The analysis shows that all datasets are of high quality and reliability.

Key findings:
	•	No missing values were detected
	•	No duplicate records were found
	•	All values are valid and positive
	•	Data structure is consistent across all companies
	•	Overall data accuracy reached 100%

Some datasets (especially Nvidia and Microsoft) contain outliers. However, in financial data this reflects real market behavior rather than errors.

Final assessment:
The data is clean, complete, consistent, and accurate, and can be reliably used for KPI analysis and further financial modeling.
